# GIT REPOSITORY MANAGEMENT RULES - MANDATORY

## 🚫 CRITICAL RESTRICTION - NO GITHUB PUSH

### **ABSOLUTE PROHIBITION - MANDATORY**
```bash
# ❌ FORBIDDEN - DO NOT EXECUTE
git push origin main
git push origin develop  
git push origin any-branch
git push --force
git push --all

# ✅ ALLOWED - Local operations only
git add .
git commit -m "message"
git branch new-branch
git checkout branch-name
git merge branch-name
```

### **WHY NO GITHUB PUSH?**
1. **Rules System Incomplete** - Must finish rules organization first
2. **Code Quality Unverified** - No validation system in place yet
3. **Documentation Missing** - API docs and database docs not ready
4. **Testing Incomplete** - No comprehensive testing completed
5. **Security Unvalidated** - Security rules not fully implemented

---

## 📋 PERMITTED GIT OPERATIONS

### **Local Development Operations - ALLOWED**
```bash
# File management
git add specific-file.ext
git add .
git reset HEAD~1

# Commit operations  
git commit -m "English only commit message"
git commit --amend

# Branch operations
git branch feature/new-feature
git checkout main
git checkout -b feature/rules-system
git merge feature-branch

# History and status
git status
git log
git diff
git show
```

### **Repository Information - ALLOWED**
```bash
# Check repository status
git remote -v
git branch -a
git log --oneline
git status --porcelain
```

