## 🛡️ ENFORCEMENT MECHANISMS

### **Pre-commit Hooks - MANDATORY**
```bash
# .git/hooks/pre-commit - MANDATORY
#!/bin/bash
echo "Checking repository rules compliance..."

# Check for rules system completion
if [ ! -f ".cursor/rules/12-tasks/current-tasks.mdc" ]; then
    echo "ERROR: Task management system not found"
    echo "Complete rules system before committing"
    exit 1
fi

# Check for Arabic text in code
if git diff --cached --name-only | xargs grep -l '[ا-ي]' 2>/dev/null; then
    echo "ERROR: Arabic text found in code"
    echo "English only policy violation"
    exit 1
fi

echo "Pre-commit checks passed"
exit 0
```

### **Pre-push Hooks - MANDATORY**
```bash
# .git/hooks/pre-push - MANDATORY
#!/bin/bash
echo "CRITICAL: GitHub push is currently PROHIBITED"
echo "Rules system must be completed first"
echo "Contact project owner for authorization"
exit 1
```

